member.name: T:Timestamps.Timestamp
member.summary: Object used to measure start, end, and total time associated with an operation.

member.name: P:Timestamps.Timestamp.Start
member.summary: The time at which the operation started. When instantiated, this is set to DateTime.UtcNow.

member.name: P:Timestamps.Timestamp.End
member.summary: The time at which the operation ended.

member.name: P:Timestamps.Timestamp.TotalMs
member.summary: The total number of milliseconds that transpired between Start and End.

member.name: P:Timestamps.Timestamp.Messages
member.summary: Log messages attached to the object by the user.
